    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this ride from day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for something that looks and drives like a total dream, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you! \u2728",
