      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance that must be seen to be believed. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections in the paintwork. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. With incredibly low mileage and a pristine undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-quality vehicle without the depreciation of a new model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
