    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle represents the definitive standard for the pre-owned market, preserved in showroom condition with meticulous attention to every mechanical and aesthetic detail. Its presentation is uncompromising, offering the discerning driver a rare opportunity to acquire a machine that remains virtually indistinguishable from its original delivery state. An investment-grade acquisition for those who demand excellence without exception.",
